chirag kahan roshni kahan ( hindi : चिराग कहाँ रोशनी कहाँ ; english : where is the lamp , where is the light is a 1959 indian bollywood film directed and produced by devendra goel . the film stars meena kumari as the protagonist ratna , and rajendra kumar , honey irani and madan puri in pivotal roles .   the film was remade in telugu as maa babu .